Subject: Re: Insight - iPad LTE
BodyText:
Hey Matt 

Hope you enjoyed the time off; you deserve it for sure. 

We do have a large LTL order with a 1 to 1 ASO AEE1448438 for qty 2,950 MD7F4LL/A IPAD WF CL 128GB SLV-USA

Doubtful we make that upper commit as units are not in this week's ship plan, might be time to get some clarity from RO adding Travis. Lucky for us Insight isn't banging my door down on this one.....yet.

Good news on the Wi-Fi only model, we shipped ~3500+ units yesterday/today due to excellent fulfillment from Apple. Insight was chuffed to bits about that. 

Thank You 



Michael McClelland 
Strategic Business Manager I 


5350 Tech Data Drive 
Clearwater, FL 33760 
864-747-7788 



﻿On 4/22/25, 1:28 PM, "Matthew Cianfoni" <mpc@apple.com <mailto:mpc@apple.com>> wrote:


This email originated outside of TD SYNNEX. Please help keep our organization and partners safe. It's up to us; think before you click.




Hi Michael,
Hope you are well. I was OOO office the past 2 business days, just catching up...


Checking in on iPad back log - looks like we have significant cellular back log
I recall a larger order was placed last week (3k) with commit date of 4/25. Will you take a look when you get a chance and provide a status update on iPad backlog?
Pls let me know if you need any escalation from me - thank you!


MC
